<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Operation_Downfall_-_Map.jpg" class="image" title="A map outlining the Japanese and U.S. (but not other Allied) ground forces scheduled to take part in the battle for Japan. Two landings were planned: (1) Olympic — the invasion of the southern island, Kyūshū, (2) Coronet — the invasion of the main island, Honshū."><img alt="A map outlining the Japanese and U.S. (but not other Allied) ground forces scheduled to take part in the battle for Japan. Two landings were planned: (1) Olympic — the invasion of the southern island, Kyūshū, (2) Coronet — the invasion of the main island, Honshū." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Operation_Downfall_-_Map.jpg/300px-Operation_Downfall_-_Map.jpg" width="300" height="231" border="0" /></a><br />
