<td colspan="2" style="width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Air_raids_on_Japan" title="Air raids on Japan">Air&#160;raids</a> – <a href="/wiki/Volcano_and_Ryukyu_Islands_campaign" title="Volcano and Ryukyu Islands campaign">Volcano&#160;&amp;&#160;Ryukyu&#160;Is</a> – <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Tokyo_in_World_War_II" title="Bombing of Tokyo in World War II" class="mw-redirect">Tokyo</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Starvation" title="Operation Starvation"><i>Starvation</i></a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Tokyo_Bay" title="Battle of Tokyo Bay">Tokyo&#160;Bay</a> – <a href="/wiki/Bombing_of_Kure_(July_1945)" title="Bombing of Kure (July 1945)">Kure</a> – <strong class="selflink"><i>Downfall</i></strong> – <a href="/wiki/Atomic_bombings_of_Hiroshima_and_Nagasaki" title="Atomic bombings of Hiroshima and Nagasaki">Hiroshima&#160;&amp;&#160;Nagasaki</a> – <a href="/wiki/Invasion_of_the_Kuril_Islands" title="Invasion of the Kuril Islands">Kurils</a></div>
</td>
