<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Douglas_J._MacEachin&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Douglas J. MacEachin (page does not exist)">MacEachin, Douglas J.</a>, "<a href="https://www.cia.gov/csi/monograph/4253605299/csi9810001.html" class="external text" title="https://www.cia.gov/csi/monograph/4253605299/csi9810001.html" rel="nofollow"><i>The Final Months of the War With Japan: Signals Intelligence, U.S. Invasion Planning, and the A-Bomb Decision</i></a>"; <a href="/wiki/CIA" title="CIA" class="mw-redirect">CIA</a> Center for the Study of Intelligence, 1998.</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Michael_D._Pearlman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Michael D. Pearlman (page does not exist)">Pearlman, Michael D.</a>, "<a href="http://www-cgsc.army.mil/carl/resources/csi/Pearlman/pearlman.asp" class="external text" title="http://www-cgsc.army.mil/carl/resources/csi/Pearlman/pearlman.asp" rel="nofollow"><i>Unconditional Surrender, Demobilization, and the Atomic Bomb</i></a>"; Combat Studies Institute, U.S. Army Command and General Staff College, 1996.</li>
<li>White, H.V., "<a href="http://cgsc.cdmhost.com/cdm4/item_viewer.php?CISOROOT=/p4013coll8&amp;CISOPTR=649&amp;CISOBOX=1&amp;REC=11" class="external text" title="http://cgsc.cdmhost.com/cdm4/item_viewer.php?CISOROOT=/p4013coll8&amp;CISOPTR=649&amp;CISOBOX=1&amp;REC=11" rel="nofollow"><i>The Japanese Plans for the Defense of Kyushu</i></a>"; <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1945-12-31"><a href="/wiki/December_31" title="December 31">31 December</a> <a href="/wiki/1945" title="1945">1945</a></span>. (link to PDF)</li>
</ul>
